Bill Gates Says States Should Rethink Pension Systems, WSJ Says

-- B y   J e r a n   W i t t e n s t e i n
-- 
2011-03-03T02:58:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-03/bill-gates-says-states-should-rethink-pension-systems-wsj-says.html
  Bill Gates , co-chair of the Bill &
Melinda Gates foundation, said U.S. states should rethink their
pension-benefits systems because the associated costs are
hurting funding for public education, the Wall Street Journal
reported, citing an interview with Gates.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
